commit_message:
Update CTCF_cohesin_shift_calculation.sh

The following basic software must be available on your system:
-PeakSplitter  version: 0.1
-bedtools version: v2.25.0

CTCF_cohesin_shift_calculation.sh

The following basic software must be available on your system.
-bedtools v2.25.0
-PeakSplitter  version: 0.1

The script requires 3 peak file in bed format and associated compressed bedgraph files. The  additional "Motif file"  is created  as discribed in "Motif oriented high-resolution analysis of ChIP-seq data reveals the topological order of CTCF and cohesin proteins on DNA" article.
